地盼望 聽見你的話語"}, {"from": 139.22,"to":143.1,"location":2, "content":"我殷切地盼望 聽見你的話語"}, {"from": 144.14,"to":149.85,"location":2, "content":"前往濃霧的對面吧"}, {"from": 149.85,"to":155.86,"location":2, "content":"在你開始徬徨之前"}, {"from": 160.07,"to":160.99,"location":2, "content":"真是的"}, {"from": 174.54,"to":175.34,"location":2, "content":"Two!"}, {"from": 179.05,"to":180.34,"location":2, "content":"Three, Two"}, {"from": 181.89,"to":185.1,"location":2, "content":"我的名字是艾莉絲"}, {"from": 185.56,"to":186.26,"location":2, "content":"來"}, {"from": 186.76,"to":191.56,"location":2, "content":"我的, 名字是, 蜜妮托娜"}, {"from": 192.31,"to":197.32,"location":2, "content":"我, 我的, 名字是, 提露塞娜"}, {"from": 197.69,"to":199.65,"location":2, "content":"妳們都很棒喔"}, {"from": 200.07,"to":202.78,"location":2, "content":"那個艾莉絲在教人學語言"}, {"from": 203.66,"to":205.37,"location":2, "content":"老師我好高興啊"}, {"from": 208.2,"to":210.62,"location":2, "content":"托娜, 差不多要到休息時間了"}, {"from": 211.46,"to":214.63,"location":2, "content":"艾莉絲閣下, 謝謝妳照顧我女兒"}, {"from": 215.29,"to":216.88,"location":2, "content":"沒有給妳添麻煩吧"}, {"from": 216.88,"to":219.34,"location":2, "content":"沒這回事, 托娜是個好孩子"}, {"from": 219.34,"to":222.43,"location":2, "content":"艾, 艾莉絲, 好痛苦喵"}, {"from": 223.3,"to":224.76,"location":2, "content":"那個戒指…"}, {"from": 224.76,"to":227.18,"location":2, "content":"確實是德路迪亞之民的證明"}, {"from": 227.18,"to":228.35,"location":2, "content":"妳是從哪裡得到那個的"}, {"from": 228.77,"to":229.68,"location":2, "content":"這個嗎"}, {"from": 229.68,"to":232.64,"location":2, "content":"基列奴在我十歲生日時送給我的"}, {"from": 233.52,"to":234.73,"location":2, "content":"基列奴?"}, {"from": 236.48,"to":240.15,"location":2, "content":"對了, 基列奴也是德路迪亞族對吧"}, {"from": 240.86,"to":243.15,"location":2, "content":"我完全忘記要問了"}, {"from": 243.57,"to":245.41,"location":2, "content":"你們認識她嗎"}, {"from": 245.7,"to":249.29,"location":2, "content":"身高很高, 跟你長得很像"}, {"from": 258.5,"to":262.38,"location":2, "content":"那傢伙…還活著嗎"}, {"from": 264.34,"to":267.43,"location":2, "content":"我還以為她已經在某處橫死街頭了"}, {"from": 268.05,"to":269.93,"location":2, "content":"請, 請等一下"}, {"from": 269.93,"to":271.89,"location":2, "content":"你跟她之間有什麼過節嗎"}, {"from": 272.27,"to":273.39,"location":2, "content":"那傢伙"}, {"from": 273.39,"to":275.85,"location":2, "content":"拋棄德路迪亞守護大森林"}, {"from": 275.85,"to":277.11,"location":2, "content":"和聖獸大人的使命"}, {"from": 277.11,"to":278.06,"location":2, "content":"爸爸"}, {"from": 278.06,"to":279.07,"location":2, "content":"從這個村子…"}, {"from": 281.07,"to":283.11,"location":2, "content":"是一族的污點"}, {"from": 284.28,"to":285.24,"location":2, "content":"你…"}, {"from": 285.57,"to":287.37,"location":2, "content":"回去了, 托娜"}, {"from": 287.37,"to":290.99,"location":2, "content":"爸爸, 好痛好痛喵"}, {"from": 302.38,"to":303.21,"location":2, "content":"艾莉絲"}, {"from": 303.46,"to":304.63,"location":2, "content":"艾莉絲"}, {"from": 305.84,"to":307.47,"location":2, "content":"你是怎樣啦"}, {"from": 314.27,"to":316.39,"location":2, "content":"基列奴是我的師傅喔"}, {"from": 316.39,"to":318.73,"location":2, "content":"是我最尊敬的人"}, {"from": 319.4,"to":321.44,"location":2, "content":"基列奴她很厲害"}, {"from": 321.82,"to":324.07,"location":2, "content":"非常…非常厲害…"}, {"from": 324.28,"to":327.32,"location":2, "content":"只要我喊救命她就會立刻趕過來"}, {"from": 327.7,"to":331.95,"location":2, "content":"速度非常快, 非常厲害"}, {"from": 332.409,"to":333.62,"location":2, "content":"基列奴…"}, {"from": 336.62,"to":337.92,"location":2, "content":"才不是…"}, {"from": 337.92,"to":339.46,"location":2, "content":"會被說這種話的…"}, {"from": 342.3,"to":345.01,"location":2, "content":"尊敬…基列奴…"}, {"from": 345.63,"to":348.26,"location":2, "content":"不, 不會吧…這怎麼可能…"}, {"from": 349.51,"to":350.85,"location":2, "content":"基列奴是…"}, {"from": 353.31,"to":356.64,"location":2, "content":"艾莉絲, 這個話題就到此為止吧"}, {"from": 357.23,"to":359.44,"location":2, "content":"為什麼…魯迪烏斯…"}, {"from": 360.65,"to":363.15,"location":2, "content":"你討厭…基列奴嗎"}, {"from": 363.69,"to":366.11,"location":2, "content":"我也喜歡基列奴喔"}, {"from": 367.15,"to":370.2,"location":2, "content":"不過我們認識的基列奴"}, {"fro